&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="conclusion-and-architecture-selection-guidelines"&gt;Conclusion and Architecture Selection Guidelines
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Recommended framework selection based on workload characteristics. Proper selection based on system requirements (latency, throughput, data volume) determines the success of the data pipeline.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Batch Processing&lt;/b&gt;: Adopt Apache Hadoop when prioritizing reliability and large-scale distributed storage (HDFS).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;In-memory Processing&lt;/b&gt;: Adopt Apache Spark when iterative calculations or high-speed data processing are required.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Real-time Streams&lt;/b&gt;: Adopt Apache Flink when low-latency stream processing and complex event processing (CEP) are required.&lt;/string&gt;&lt;/string&gt;&lt;/void&gt;&lt;/string&gt;&lt;/string&gt;&lt;/dataentry&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>